### Normalizer REST-client test suite
###
### NOTE on URLs:
### - This file targets http://localhost:8001/analyze-ticket as specified
###   (BACKEND_CONTRACT.md §2 "Host port for my own testing").
### - The compose service binds container port 9000 with no host-port
###   mapping; if you run locally via uvicorn, the service listens on 9000.
###   To use 8001 locally, run:
###     uvicorn normalizer.app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8001
###   Or update the URL below.
###
### Health probe
GET http://localhost:8001/health
Accept: application/json

###

