### ══ STAGE 1 TESTS (cleaner)
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### T01 — Bangla complaint with amount — Stage1 — Evidence Reasoning
POST http://localhost:8001/analyze-ticket
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ticket_id": "T01",
  "complaint": "আমি ভুল নম্বরে ৫০০০ টাকা পাঠিয়েছি সকাল ১০টায়",
  "language": "bn",
  "channel": "in_app_chat",
  "user_type": "customer",
  "transaction_history": [
    {
      "transaction_id": "TXN-T01",
      "timestamp": "2026-04-14T10:08:22Z",
      "type": "transfer",
      "amount": 5000,
      "counterparty": "+8801799999999",
      "status": "completed"
    }
  ]
}

# Expected: relevant_transaction_id=TXN-T01, evidence_verdict=consistent,
#           case_type=wrong_transfer, severity=high (or critical — 5000 < 10000
#           so high is the default for wrong_transfer), department=dispute_resolution,
#           human_review_required=true (wrong_transfer + consistent → True per
#           precedence rule)

###

